# Design documents

Follow [.notebook/06_design/README.md](../../.notebook/06_design/README.md).

## Basic vs Detail

| Type | Folder | Skills |
|------|--------|--------|
| Basic | `basic-design/` | `design-workflow` |
| Detail | `detail-design/` | `design-workflow` |

## Rules

- Copy từ `_*.template.md` trong `basic-design/`; bỏ prefix `_` khi tạo bản chính thức
- Link design files từ `.backlogs/{id}/design/{id}.md` mục **Artifacts**
- Do not duplicate full acceptance criteria — reference backlog task
- Comments in code: English. Design docs for PM/client: project language (often Vietnamese)
